{"title":"中国民主促进会成立四十五周年  纪念献词","authors":["赵朴初"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":12,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国民主促进会成立四十五周年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纪念献词"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵朴初"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四十五年过去了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纪念过去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是为着现在，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为着将来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不忘记"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反饥饿！反内战！反独裁！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈烈轰轰的上海。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不忘记"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请愿到南京下关，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们马老遭受的迫害。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不忘记"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一切，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们民进诞生前后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全中国的怒潮澎湃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在共产党领导下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民终于推翻三座大山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站立了起来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高举社会主义大旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建设新中国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"改造旧世界。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立志于振兴中华，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从不怕风狂浪骇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作为参政党的民进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们应当"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无愧于过去的光荣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们应当"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无负于今天的时代。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个教师占多数的政党"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更应当"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把心血献给人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把光热献给后代。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勇猛精进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丝毫不怠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任凭岁月的迁流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百折千回终不改！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九九○年十二月"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}